targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
    t,
    groupArray((concat('Computed TEC ', sat, ' ', sigcomb), nt)) AS groupArr
FROM
(
    SELECT
        (intDiv(time, (1000)) *(1000)) AS t,
        sat,
        sigcomb,
        avg(nt) nt
    FROM computed.NT final

    WHERE
        $timeFilterMs
        AND sat IN ($satellite)
    GROUP BY
        t,
        sat,
        sigcomb
    ORDER BY
        t,
        sat
)
GROUP BY t

ORDER BY t
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT
    t,
    groupArray((concat('Computed TEC ', sat, ' ', sigcomb), nt)) AS groupArr
FROM
(
    SELECT
        (intDiv(time, (1000)) *(1000)) AS t,
        sat,
        sigcomb,
        avg(nt) nt
    FROM computed.NT final

    WHERE
        "d" >= toDate(1679293432) AND "d" <= toDate(1679304232) AND time >= toUInt64(1679293432634/1000 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1679304232634/1000 * 1000)
        AND sat IN ('GPS6','GPS11','GPS12','GLONASS13','GLONASS14','GPS17','GPS19','GLONASS24','GPS24')
    GROUP BY
        t,
        sat,
        sigcomb
    ORDER BY
        t,
        sat
)
GROUP BY t

ORDER BY t
